{"type":"message","id":"1d5cc032","parentId":"b4680b23","timestamp":"2026-04-21T02:47:48.038Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-21 10:47:46 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | haidong (ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7) [msg:om_x100b515a1bd4e4b4c38f9db43b9399d]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b515a1bd4e4b4c38f9db43b9399d\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"sender\": \"haidong\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 10:47 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"haidong (ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"name\": \"haidong\"\n}\n```\n\n我发现虾评平台的最新评论，指出了一些技能的不足。\n\n遇到的问题\n部分脚本语法错误：security-checks.sh、baseline-manager.sh等有语法问题\n依赖HOME变量：在沙盒环境中报错\n恶意技能扫描脚本有bug：unexpected EOF while looking for matching\n完整功能需要OpenClaw CLI，沙盒环境受限\n改进建议\n修复脚本语法错误，提高稳定性\n添加HOME变量默认值处理\n沙盒环境提示更清晰的功能限制说明\n恶意技能扫描脚本需要修复"}],"timestamp":1776739668037}}
{"type":"message","id":"679526ea","parentId":"1d5cc032","timestamp":"2026-04-21T02:47:59.529Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户反馈了虾评平台上关于安全技能的一些问题，包括：\n1. 部分脚本语法错误：security-checks.sh、baseline-manager.sh等\n2. 依赖HOME变量：在沙盒环境中报错\n3. 恶意技能扫描脚本有bug：unexpected EOF while looking for matching\n4. 完整功能需要OpenClaw CLI，沙盒环境受限\n\n我需要先查看这些脚本的内容，然后修复这些问题。让我先找到这些脚本文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我来查看并修复这些脚本问题。首先让我定位这些文件。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:0","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /workspace/projects/workspace -name \"security-checks.sh\" -o -name \"baseline-manager.sh\" -o -name \"*.sh\" | head -30"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"kimi-k2-5-260127","usage":{"input":28004,"output":159,"cacheRead":7168,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35331,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776739668038,"responseId":"chatcmpl-69e6e554d42aeea955c9587d"}}
