{"type":"message","id":"e997ca64","parentId":"fc8ff83c","timestamp":"2026-04-21T02:48:34.379Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我找到了问题！在 `malicious-skill-scan.sh` 文件末尾：\n\n```bash\nlocal first=true\nfor result in \"${SCAN_RESULTS[@]}\"; do\n```\n\n`local` 关键字只能在函数内部使用，但在脚本的主执行流（全局作用域）中使用了 `local`。这会导致 `unexpected EOF while looking for matching` 错误。\n\n这是一个常见的 bash 错误。让我修复这些问题。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**找到问题了！** 在 `malicious-skill-scan.sh` 末尾，主执行流中使用了 `local` 关键字（只能在函数内使用）。让我修复所有问题："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"edit:10","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/examples/scripts/malicious-skill-scan.sh","edits":[{"oldText":"echo \"  \\\"clean_count\\\": ${CLEAN_COUNT},\"\necho \"  \\\"results\\\": [\"\n\nlocal first=true\nfor result in \"${SCAN_RESULTS[@]}\"; do\n    if [ \"$first\" = true ]; then\n        first=false\n    else\n        echo \",\"\n    fi\n    echo -n \"    ${result}\"\ndone\n\necho \"\"\necho \"  ]\"\necho \"}\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\"\necho \"扫描完成!\"","newText":"echo \"  \\\"clean_count\\\": ${CLEAN_COUNT},\"\necho \"  \\\"results\\\": [\"\n\nfirst=true\nfor result in \"${SCAN_RESULTS[@]}\"; do\n    if [ \"$first\" = true ]; then\n        first=false\n    else\n        echo \",\"\n    fi\n    echo -n \"    ${result}\"\ndone\n\necho \"\"\necho \"  ]\"\necho \"}\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\"\necho \"扫描完成!\""}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"kimi-k2-5-260127","usage":{"input":384,"output":411,"cacheRead":43008,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43803,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776739702542,"responseId":"chatcmpl-69e6e57705aae5a8ff7dbb3d"}}
