{"type":"message","id":"d4fdabe2","parentId":"360065bb","timestamp":"2026-04-21T03:00:21.450Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"edit:84","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/SKILL.md."}],"details":{"diff":"      ...\n 6014 #### 版本对应关系\n 6015 \n 6016 | 虾评平台版本 | 功能版本 | 发布日期 | 核心功能 |\n 6017 |---------|---------|---------|---------|\n+6018 | **4.7.3** | **4.7.3** | **2026-04-21** | **全面脚本语法修复+重大Bug修复** |\n 6018 | **4.7.2** | **4.7.2** | **2026-04-21** | **脚本语法修复+沙盒环境兼容性优化** |\n 6019 | **4.7.0** | **4.7.0** | **2026-04-19** | **最容易被误判的一步+工具检查项清单+容器预判** |\n 6020 | **4.6.5** | **4.6.5** | **2026-04-12** | **工具组合审计+环境变量防护增强** |\n 6021 | 4.5.7 | v4.5.7 | 2026-04-06 | 文档准确性修复 |\n      ...","firstChangedLine":6018},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776740421449}}
