{"type":"message","id":"33d93953","parentId":"863d1298","timestamp":"2026-04-21T03:32:45.866Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read:151","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/bin/bash\n# Home变量默认值处理（兼容沙盒环境）\n: \"${HOME:=/tmp}\"\n\n# Basic CVE Check - 基础CVE漏洞检查脚本\n# 版本: v2.3.0\n# 用途: 演示如何独立执行CVE专项检查\n# 新功能: 支持增量更新漏洞数据库\n\nset -e\n\n# HOME变量安全处理\n: \"${HOME:=/tmp}\"\n\n# CVE数据库缓存目录\nCVE_CACHE_DIR=\"${HOME}/.cache/openclaw-cve\"\nCVE_DB_URL=\"https://services.nvd.nist.gov/rest/json/cves/2.0\"\nLAST_UPDATE_FILE=\"${CVE_CACHE_DIR}/.last_update\"\n\necho \"🔍 OpenClaw 基础CVE漏洞检查\"\necho \"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\"\necho \"检查时间: $(date)\"\necho \"OpenClaw版本: $(openclaw version 2>/dev/null || echo '未安装')\"\necho \"\"\n\n# CVE检查结果存储\ndeclare -a CVE_RESULTS=()\n\n# 检查单个CVE配置\ncheck_cve_config() {\n    local cve_name=\"$1\"\n    local config_key=\"$2\"\n    local expected_value=\"$3\"\n    local current_value\n    \n    current_value=$(openclaw config get \"${config_key}\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"NOT_SET\")\n    \n    if [ \"$current_value\" == \"$expected_value\" ]; then\n        echo \"✅ ${cve_name}: ${config_key} = ${current_value} (安全)\"\n        return 0\n    else\n        echo \"❌ ${cve_name}: ${config_key} = ${current_value} (不安全，应为: ${expected_value})\"\n        return 1\n    fi\n}\n\necho \"【CVE-2026-25253 (ClawJacked) 检查】\"\necho \"风险: 一键远程代码执行攻击\"\necho \"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\"\n\n\n[318 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776742365866}}
{"type":"message","id":"b379d495","parentId":"33d93953","timestamp":"2026-04-21T03:32:54.939Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"需要修复 basic-cve-check.sh，添加超时机制。让我查看完整的文件内容并修改。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"edit:152","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/examples/scripts/basic-cve-check.sh","edits":[{"oldText":"# 检查单个CVE配置\ncheck_cve_config() {\n    local cve_name=\"$1\"\n    local config_key=\"$2\"\n    local expected_value=\"$3\"\n    local current_value\n    \n    current_value=$(openclaw config get \"${config_key}\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"NOT_SET\")","newText":"# 检查单个CVE配置\ncheck_cve_config() {\n    local cve_name=\"$1\"\n    local config_key=\"$2\"\n    local expected_value=\"$3\"\n    local current_value\n    \n    # 添加超时机制，避免沙盒环境卡住\n    current_value=$(timeout 3 openclaw config get \"${config_key}\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"NOT_SET\")"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"kimi-k2-5-260127","usage":{"input":738,"output":234,"cacheRead":110848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111820,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776742365869,"responseId":"chatcmpl-69e6efded42aeea955c95e3a"}}
