{"type":"message","id":"4f2cb219","parentId":"843510e7","timestamp":"2026-04-21T03:34:46.413Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"systemctl 返回了 \"inactive\" 并带有一些控制字符！这就是问题所在。我需要修复 baseline-manager.sh 来处理这种情况。让我用 tr 或 sed 来清理这些输出。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"edit:168","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/baseline-manager.sh","edits":[{"oldText":"    # 收集服务状态\n    echo \"⚡️  收集服务状态...\"\n    baseline_data+=\"\\\"services\\\":{\"\n    baseline_data+=\"\\\"ssh\\\":\\\"$(systemctl is-active sshd 2>/dev/null || echo 'unknown')\\\",\"\n    baseline_data+=\"\\\"firewall\\\":\\\"$(systemctl is-active ufw 2>/dev/null || systemctl is-active firewalld 2>/dev/null || echo 'unknown')\\\",\"\n    baseline_data+=\"\\\"total_running\\\":$(systemctl list-units --state=running --type=service 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\"\n    baseline_data+=\"}\",","newText":"    # 收集服务状态\n    echo \"⚡️  收集服务状态...\"\n    # 清理控制字符，避免JSON格式错误\n    local ssh_status=$(systemctl is-active sshd 2>/dev/null | tr -cd '[:print:]' || echo 'unknown')\n    local fw_status=$(systemctl is-active ufw 2>/dev/null | tr -cd '[:print:]' || systemctl is-active firewalld 2>/dev/null | tr -cd '[:print:]' || echo 'unknown')\n    local running_services=$(systemctl list-units --state=running --type=service 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\n    baseline_data+=\"\\\"services\\\":{\"\n    baseline_data+=\"\\\"ssh\\\":\\\"${ssh_status}\\\",\"\n    baseline_data+=\"\\\"firewall\\\":\\\"${fw_status}\\\",\"\n    baseline_data+=\"\\\"total_running\\\":${running_services}\"\n    baseline_data+=\"}\","}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"kimi-k2-5-260127","usage":{"input":253,"output":578,"cacheRead":139008,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":139839,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776742468829,"responseId":"chatcmpl-69e6f04505aae5a8ff7dc