{"type":"compaction","id":"ee4c2058","parentId":"fd056f93","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:22:16.122Z","summary":"## Goal\n1. Fix script syntax errors reported by Shapingping platform users\n2. Verify ALL scripts pass syntax checks (comprehensive audit)\n3. Publish to Shapingping platform first, then sync version to GitHub (version consistency workflow)\n4. Evaluate skill in Coze sandbox environment to identify CLI dependency issues\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- **Version workflow**: Shapingping first → get version → sync local SKILL.md → commit to GitHub with matching tag\n- **Sandbox compatibility**: Skill should work in environments with limited CLI access\n- **All scripts must pass** `bash -n` syntax check before publishing\n- **Strict Bash rules**: `local` keyword ONLY inside functions, not in main execution flow\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Fixed malicious-skill-scan.sh: Removed `local` keywords from main execution flow (line 228, line 159 in for loop)\n- [x] Fixed security-audit.sh: Changed heredoc from `<< 'EOF'` to `<< EOF` for variable expansion\n- [x] Added HOME variable default to basic-cve-check.sh and malicious-skill-scan.sh\n- [x] **Comprehensive audit**: Found and fixed 4 additional critical syntax errors:\n  - dashboard/api.sh: Complete rewrite (else without if, undefined function, case statement error)\n  - ai-analyzer/anomaly_detector.sh: Simplified rewrite (unclosed quotes/brackets in awk/bc commands)\n  - threat-response/playbooks/rate-limit.sh: Complete rewrite (orphaned fi, garbled redirection)\n  - threat_playbook_manager.sh: Fixed regex escaping (escaped semicolon)\n- [x] All 24 scripts pass `bash -n` syntax check\n- [x] Published to Shapingping (version 4.7.2 assigned)\n- [x] Synced SKILL.md and GitHub tag to 4.7.2\n- [x] **Sandbox evaluation**: Identified issues in Coze environment\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Commit and push sandbox-related fixes (malicious-skill-scan.sh loop local vars, baseline-manager.sh JSON cleanup, container-detector.sh timeout, shebang fixes)\n\n### Blocked\n- [None]\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Version workflow**: Must publish to Shapingping FIRST to get auto-assigned version, then update local files (user explicitly stated: \"以后先发布到虾评，然后获取虾评的版本号\")\n- **Complete rewrites preferred**: For severely broken files (api.sh, anomaly_detector.sh, rate-limit.sh) rather than piecemeal fixes\n- **Sandbox timeout strategy**: Add `timeout` commands for potentially blocking operations like `capsh --print`\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Commit sandbox-related fixes to GitHub\n2. User to decide if these sandbox fixes warrant a new Shapingping release (4.7.3)\n3. Document sandbox limitations in SKILL.md or README\n\n## Critical Context\n- **Shapingping API**: \n  - Upload: POST https://xiaping.coze.site/api/upload\n  - API Key: sk_N0wcqRIDDt_Py_rz8O7plGO8EKL1Lmmp\n  - Skill ID: 61c9999f-1794-4f55-a6b8-6e457376b51e\n- **Current version**: 4.7.2 (consistent across Shapingping, SKILL.md, GitHub)\n- **Repository**: https://github.com/zhanghaidong-dalian/openclaw-healthcheck-skill.git\n\n- **Sandbox issues identified**:\n  - `malicious-skill-scan.sh`: `local` keyword used in for loop at line 159 (fixed but not yet committed)\n  - `baseline-manager.sh`: `jq` parse error \"control characters from U+0000 through U+001F\" from `ip -j` output (fixed with `tr -d '\\000-\\037'`)\n  - `container-detector.sh`: `capsh --print` hangs (fixed with `timeout 2`)\n  - `basic-cve-check.sh`: Depends on `openclaw config get` which may hang (needs timeout)\n  - `drift-detector.sh`, `backup-functions.sh`: shebang position fixed (not yet committed)\n\n- **Files already modified for sandbox fixes** (uncommitted):\n  - `/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/examples/scripts/malicious-skill-scan.sh`\n  - `/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/baseline-manager.sh`\n  - `/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/container-detector.sh`\n  - `/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/drift-detector.sh`\n  - `/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/backup-functions.sh`\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Original Request\nUser (haidong) requested: \"按照修复建议执行\" (Execute according to the fix recommendations)\n\n## Early Progress\nThe AI assistant identified and executed the following fix recommendations for the healthcheck-skill project:\n\n1. **Timeout mechanisms** - Added `timeout` command to prevent hanging scripts\n2. **Variable scope fixes** - Removed `local` keywords from main execution flow (only allowed inside functions)\n3. **JSON output sanitization** - Used `tr` to remove control characters causing JSON parse errors\n4. **Empty output handling** - Added fallback values when commands return empty results\n5. **Script exit handling** - Added `|| true` to prevent premature script exits\n\n## Context for Suffix\nThe assistant completed fixes to three key scripts:\n- `basic-cve-check.sh` - Added 3-second timeout to `openclaw` commands\n- `baseline-manager.sh` - Fixed JSON parsing errors caused by control characters in `systemctl` and `ss` command outputs\n- `container-detector.sh` - Fixed script exiting early when not running in container environment\n\nAll 25 shell scripts in the project passed syntax validation. The conversation ended with a comprehensive syntax check showing all scripts validated successfully.\n\n<read-files>\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/env-leak-detector.sh\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/one-click-hardening.sh\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/workspace/projects/workspace/MEMORY.md\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/FIXES-v4.7.2.md\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/SKILL.md\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/dashboard/api.sh\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/examples/scripts/basic-cve-check.sh\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/examples/scripts/malicious-skill-scan.sh\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/ai-analyzer/anomaly_detector.sh\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/backup-functions.sh\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/baseline-manager.sh\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/container-detector.sh\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/drift-detector.sh\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/threat-response/playbooks/rate-limit.sh\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/threat-response/threat_playbook_manager.sh\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/security-audit.sh\n</modified-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"d77964e0","tokensBefore":187329,"details":{"readFiles":["/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/env-leak-detector.sh","/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/one-click-hardening.sh"],"modifiedFiles":["/workspace/projects/workspace/MEMORY.md","/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/FIXES-v4.7.2.md","/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/SKILL.md","/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/dashboard/api.sh","/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/examples/scripts/basic-cve-check.sh","/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/examples/scripts/malicious-skill-scan.sh","/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/ai-analyzer/anomaly_detector.sh","/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/backup-functions.sh","/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/baseline-manager.sh","/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/container-detector.sh","/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/drift-detector.sh","/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/threat-response/playbooks/rate-limit.sh","/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/threat-response/threat_playbook_manager.sh","/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/se